radiographic_examinations.procedure_name: CT scan of the abdomen and pelvis
radiographic_examinations.findings: Bilateral, punctate, nonobstructing renal calculi without hydronephrosis. No evidence of bowel obstruction or acute inflammation. Normal premenopausal ovaries containing functional follicles.
Clear lungs, normal cardiac silhouette, no pulmonary edema, and no mediastinal or hilar lymphadenopathy.
